                            Account Type
                        </h2>
                        <p2>Select your account type *</p2>
                        <br />
                    </div>
                    <div class="account-icon">
                        <a href="#" id="Individual">
                            <div class="radio_individual">
                                <span class="acc-icon-text">Individual</span>
                            </div>
